	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi literas tuas, chare frater, et inter turbas varias et multiplices brevibus tibi respondeo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Placet relatio, quae passim per <persName type="auto_name">Rhetiam</persName> denunciatur communitatibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tua vero epistola displicet per omnia, non quod scripta sit per te, et quatenus te attinet, sed quatenus attinet [iniusticiam, perfidiam et corruptelam]<note type="margin">a.R.: ...</note> Dominum oro, ut in his difficultatibus vobis consulat et medeatur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video<note type="margin">a.R.: ...</note> [...]</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hac septimana transiit hac illustrissimus princeps d. <persName type="auto_name">Christophorus</persName>, dux Bavariae Palatinus, electoris filius, iuvenis 17 annorum.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Studuit <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevae</placeName>, per <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName> ad nos venit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amicissime et honorificentissime exceptus et dimissus abiit <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileam</placeName> comitatus nostris et <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernatibus</placeName> quibusdam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Princeps est spei maximae; dominus benedicat illi!</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit hisce quoque diebus d. <persName type="auto_name">Petrus Dathenus</persName>; quid egerit, intelliges ex hoc apposito scripto.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oravit, ut te hortarer c[auss]ae adsis et, si quem noris, qui opibus polleat, ipsi hortator sis, ut aliquid conferat.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu itaque fungere boni nuncii munere et responde, si quid sit spei.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicta sunt comitia Aaroviam 4 urbibus Tigurinae, <placeName type="auto_name">Bernati</placeName>, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensi</placeName> et <placeName type="auto_name">Schaffhusianae</placeName> ad 8. augusti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt de novo conflixisse ad Groningam copias et rursus circiter 300 Albanorum<note type="margin">a.R.: eigtl. <placeName type="auto_name">Albarum</placeName> geschr.</note> desideratos; Albanum misisse eo Scipionem Vitellium; ipsum delitescere in munitissima arce Hertzogenbusch; venire item ex Hispania et Italia copias novas.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo praetextu occiderit <persName type="auto_name">Egmundanum</persName>, habes hic.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der tütschen rüttern rittmeister, so in Franckrych xin under <persName type="auto_name">Casimiro</persName> und <persName type="auto_name">hertzog Wilhelmen</persName>, die besten habend sich versprochen Uraniensi.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Claus</persName> von <placeName type="auto_name">Hattstatt</placeName> fuͤrt imm zuͦ ein regiment lantzknecht und sunst ein graff ouch ein regiment, item ein fryherr uß <placeName ref="l691" cert="high">Lothringen</placeName> uff 4000 Gaschgonyer und Franzosen; werdent 1. augusti an der Maaß sin, und wirt grosser ernst angewendt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott der allmächtig gäbe gnad; dann es sin gar wol bedarff.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Bättend ouch gott trüwlich.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Gruͤssend mir die 3 herren burgermeister, <foreign xml:lang="la">h. <persName type="auto_name">Carolum</persName>, <persName ref="p2627" cert="high">Pontisellam</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Ganthnerum</persName>, omnes.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 30. iulii 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
